[
    {
        "text": "Mayonnaise, but don't be scared of making it.",
        "startTime": 6099,
        "endTime": 8254,
        "slowStartTime": 9299,
        "slowEndTime": 12606
    },
    {
        "text": "Basically all it is is emulsification of raw egg yolks and groundnut oil.",
        "startTime": 8534,
        "endTime": 12159,
        "slowStartTime": 12951,
        "slowEndTime": 18464
    },
    {
        "text": "Groundnut oil because it's a neutral oil, it's not flavored.",
        "startTime": 12387,
        "endTime": 15135,
        "slowStartTime": 18730,
        "slowEndTime": 22927
    },
    {
        "text": "Three egg yolks, teaspoon of English mustard.",
        "startTime": 16158,
        "endTime": 19620,
        "slowStartTime": 24387,
        "slowEndTime": 29655
    },
    {
        "text": "And the mustard gives the mayonnaise a little bit of heat.",
        "startTime": 19971,
        "endTime": 21777,
        "slowStartTime": 30107,
        "slowEndTime": 32890
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, lid on.",
        "startTime": 22909,
        "endTime": 23627,
        "slowStartTime": 34513,
        "slowEndTime": 35666
    },
    {
        "text": "If you haven't got a mixer, you can whisk it by hand but this is a lot quicker.",
        "startTime": 23977,
        "endTime": 27084,
        "slowStartTime": 36115,
        "slowEndTime": 40851
    },
    {
        "text": "Once you've mixed it, this is where it's really important that we add the oil slowly.",
        "startTime": 29777,
        "endTime": 34221,
        "slowStartTime": 44815,
        "slowEndTime": 51556
    },
    {
        "text": "The first 30 seconds of making a mayonnaise is the most crucial.",
        "startTime": 34921,
        "endTime": 37172,
        "slowStartTime": 52532,
        "slowEndTime": 55983
    },
    {
        "text": "Slowly with the oil, that stops it from splitting.",
        "startTime": 37481,
        "endTime": 40566,
        "slowStartTime": 56372,
        "slowEndTime": 61074
    },
    {
        "text": "This is 300 ml of groundnut oil.",
        "startTime": 42679,
        "endTime": 44621,
        "slowStartTime": 64169,
        "slowEndTime": 67156
    },
    {
        "text": "Drizzle into the eggs.",
        "startTime": 44952,
        "endTime": 46425,
        "slowStartTime": 67578,
        "slowEndTime": 69862
    },
    {
        "text": "And you never season mayonnaise until the end.",
        "startTime": 48313,
        "endTime": 50337,
        "slowStartTime": 72619,
        "slowEndTime": 75730
    },
    {
        "text": "When you season it to begin with, it destroys the egg yolks.",
        "startTime": 50781,
        "endTime": 53834,
        "slowStartTime": 76321,
        "slowEndTime": 80976
    },
    {
        "text": "Now we can add the oil a little bit quicker.",
        "startTime": 54511,
        "endTime": 56243,
        "slowStartTime": 81917,
        "slowEndTime": 84589
    },
    {
        "text": "You can just hear that sound when it goes from liquid to really nice, thick mayonnaise.",
        "startTime": 57076,
        "endTime": 62959,
        "slowStartTime": 85764,
        "slowEndTime": 94663
    },
    {
        "text": "Now season it, salt, pepper, fresh lemon juice.",
        "startTime": 65659,
        "endTime": 74019,
        "slowStartTime": 98638,
        "slowEndTime": 111253
    },
    {
        "text": "That gives it a really nice sort of zesty freshness, makes it exuberant.",
        "startTime": 74436,
        "endTime": 78858,
        "slowStartTime": 111804,
        "slowEndTime": 118512
    },
    {
        "text": "And then just a quick blast.",
        "startTime": 80221,
        "endTime": 81559,
        "slowStartTime": 120482,
        "slowEndTime": 122563
    },
    {
        "text": "And what we're looking for is this really nice, soft, creamy textured mayonnaise.",
        "startTime": 83963,
        "endTime": 89422,
        "slowStartTime": 126094,
        "slowEndTime": 134358
    },
    {
        "text": "Beautiful!",
        "startTime": 89635,
        "endTime": 90042,
        "slowStartTime": 134603,
        "slowEndTime": 135288
    },
    {
        "text": "Looks fantastic and tastes delicious.",
        "startTime": 90436,
        "endTime": 93347,
        "slowStartTime": 135804,
        "slowEndTime": 140245
    },
    {
        "text": "Right.",
        "startTime": 93705,
        "endTime": 94075,
        "slowStartTime": 140708,
        "slowEndTime": 141337
    },
    {
        "text": "Keep it in the fridge.",
        "startTime": 94353,
        "endTime": 95412,
        "slowStartTime": 141680,
        "slowEndTime": 143343
    }
]